        {
          "context": "使用CIFS时，`nfs-common`，`cifs-utils`是必须的前置软件（在Ubuntu发行版下），安装命令为：`sudo apt install -y nfs-common cifs-utils`。",
          "qas": [
            {
              "id": "5-340-1",
              "question": "使用CIFS时需要安装哪些前置软件？",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "`nfs-common`，`cifs-utils`",
                  "answer_start": 6
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "5-340-2",
              "question": "安装CIFS所需前置软件的命令是什么？",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "`sudo apt install -y nfs-common cifs-utils`",
                  "answer_start": 53
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "context": "使用CIFS时，需编辑`/etc/fstab`文件，命令为`sudo deepin-deitor /etc/fstab`，添加内容为：//your_nas_ip/dir /mnt/NAS/dir cifs rw,dir_mode=0777,file_mode=0777,vers=2.0,username=yourusername,password=yourpassword 0 0，其中`your_nas_ip`代表NAS的访问地址，`dir`代表NAS下的分享挂载点，`/mnt/mountdir`代表本设备要挂载到的路径，`yourusername`为访问的用户名，`yourpassword`为访问用户的密码，若匿名访问则不需要username与password并改为`guest`。",
          "qas": [
            {
              "id": "5-340-3",
              "question": "使用CIFS时需要编辑哪个文件？",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "`/etc/fstab`",
                  "answer_start": 17
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "5-340-4",
              "question": "编辑`/etc/fstab`文件的命令是什么？",
              "answers": [
                {
                  "text": "`sudo deepin-deitor /etc/fstab`",
                  "answer_start": 34
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "id": "5-340-5",
